searchConfiguration.description:
@DirtiesContext will force Spring to reload the context after the test. It can be very slow and it is not necessary in most of the cases.

You can find more information : https://www.notion.so/m33/BFB-CA-R-duction-du-temps-de-CI-9fd4ef2924da401390835733c0567d54

You can remove this warning by adding on your class : @SuppressWarnings("AllowDirtiesContext")
